  • Classes in com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.plan used by com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.internal.command.plan 
    Class and Description
    PlanGetCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to get the details of a Plan.
    PlanGetResponse
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a PlanGetCommand, describing the details of the retrieved Plan.
    PlanListCommand
    Command sent from a DNSAPIClient to the DNSAPI server, to get a list of searched Plans.
    PlanListResponse
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a PlanListCommand, returning the list of retrieved PlanRecords.
